Application: Cascade Self-Reference
  Description: Self-referencing cascade for tree-delete semantics
Id: a1c0c1a0-cade-4a00-9000-000000000002

Identity:
  Scopes are "tree.view", "tree.manage", "tree.delete"
  A "tester" has "tree.view", "tree.manage", and "tree.delete"

Content called "tree nodes":
  Each tree node has a label which is text, required
  Each tree node has a parent which references tree nodes, cascade on delete
  Anyone with "tree.view" can view tree nodes
  Anyone with "tree.manage" can create tree nodes
  Anyone with "tree.delete" can delete tree nodes
